Borden Avenue, at the S. W. corner of 48th Street, showing an old house, view 3 being east from 47th Street. The house stands in the direct path of 53rd Avenue, which meets Borden Avenue and 48th Street here.

Eugene L.Armbruster Collection
View 1: June, 1924
Views 2,3: March, 1925
